Signature for building verbose new PAATState object (we don't make defensive copies of the context set for performance reasons, so be aware)

Parameters:
iContext - context
iAFP - action free prefix position in AST
iAFPE - action free prefix end position in AST
iIsAFP - determines if current navigation is by Action Free Prefix
iPosition - position in parent context
iLast - last position in parent context
iProtect - determines if the document containing context is protected or not
numHigher - number of Kleene star iterations to perform by inner actions (only applicable to final inner action inside each Kleene star)
currAction - the id of the current action
